snippet.title: Gunkprotocol (June Flower, 2023, Windows) Walkthrough
snippet.description:
Tiny indie exploration game made in Godot with a mystery package in the game's files.
Check it out here. https://june-flower.itch.io/gunkprotocol

"Gunkprotocol is a small top-down exploration game I made to learn GodotTurns out I despise programming so much that I honestly might not use that knowledge ever again, but at least something came out of it

Story:
Primordial waters laced with microplastics
Red metal spires cage the the holy soil forevermore
Anger festers under the mud mounds, deep below the ground
A signal runs through the smoke-filled orbit, all the way from Ceres straight to old coughing Earth
A data delivery blobot moves its joint for the first time in centuries

Credits:
Everything by June Flower except for...
Collision code help by NarfNRA
Some testing by John Thyer and Millie 'Bjorknfork' Milliemillie"

- - -

meow :3
